  "texts": [
    "It is important to evaluate the impact of initial strategies and make the necessary changes.",
    "An audit and feedback strategy can be used to assess the change brought about by the intervention compared to the pre-intervention situation.",
    "Although this strategy may be complex and timeconsuming, it is an effective way to assess progress and make necessary corrections.",
    "The audit results can determine whether to maintain current actions or adapt the intervention.",
    "If necessary, the education and guidance cycle can be renewed to increase effectiveness."
